年8月診斷患上肝癌併發症，最後在1997年11月底病逝，葉劉淑儀自此獨力支撐家庭"},{"pid":"6be2b06d2ec875a0ade07b5ef83b0ac1a3a3f4a6","tid":1183724,"uid":29080,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T07:21:17.000Z","msg":"唔好燒妹仔<br />\n怕會喺地府包二奶"},{"pid":"cfb881a6b73570c05f0a4936e6624cb7371ccb37","tid":1183724,"uid":18251,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T07:24:31.000Z","msg":"保皇黨就係得啲咁嘅質素<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cf446e68e8358bece5073745fcb49d62b0f775a","tid":1183724,"uid":30633,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T07:24:56.000Z","msg":"助攻王again"},{"pid":"bdfbec609a20239332c765751dd4c3398cf1bf19","tid":1183724,"uid":63154,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T07:27:06.000Z","msg":"唔抵得師奶有個完整家庭？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52d8a33ed864a66993a6ed3d8554af468bc48a54","tid":1183724,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T08:00:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f5eabf7713066d0f63d81e572a4cd927589d6fc","tid":1183724,"uid":134474,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"quote":{"pid":"09afe95ffd0ee3d4a36f9d94e660c1fc09992eb4","tid":1183724,"uid":78947,"like":311,"dislike":0,"score":311,"quote":{"pid":"b29923c42404dbfc235c83efd3c0f2e887012dc8","tid":1183724,"uid":160605,"like":405,"dislike":5,"score":400,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T06:50:22.000Z","msg":"葉劉我祝你老公包二奶三奶四奶～～"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T06:51:14.000Z","msg":"冇咁嘅機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T08:02:59.000Z","msg":"呢條賤婦剋夫命"},{"pid":"77c9ac5080d7308069f6b01650bb68934ba73523","tid":1183724,"uid":33730,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T08:04:30.000Z","msg":"你老公連包二奶既機會都無呀<im